  "passageParts": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Harlan Coben believes that if you're a writer, you'll find the time; and that if you can't find the time, then writing isn't a priority and you're not a writer. For him, writing is a\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\njob, a job like any other. He has\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nit with plumbing, pointing out that a plumber doesn't wake up and say that he can't work with pipes today.\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​, like most writers these days, you're holding down a job to pay the bills, it's not\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nto find the time to write. But it's not impossible. It requires determination and single - mindedness.\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nthat most bestselling authors began writing when they were doing other things to earn a living. And today, even writers who are fairly\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\noften have to do other work to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\ntheir writing income.\n As Harlan Coben has suggested it's a\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nof priorities. To make writing a priority, you'll have to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nSome of your day - to - day activities and some things you really enjoy. Depending on your\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nand your lifestyle, that might mean spending less time watching television or listening to music, though some people can write\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nthey listen to music. You might have to\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nthe amount of exercise or sport you do. You'll have to make social media an\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 13
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nactivity rather than a daily, time - consuming\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 14
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​. There'll probably have to be less socializing with your friends and less time with your family. It's a\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nlearning curve, and it won't always make you popular.\n There's just one thing you should try to keep at least some time for,\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nyour writing and that's reading. Any writer needs to read as much and as widely as they can; it's the one\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 17
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nsupporter - Something you can't do without.\n Time is finite. The older you get, the\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 18
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nit seems to go. We need to use it as carefully and as\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 19
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\nas we can, that means prioritizing out activities so that we spend most time on the things we really want to do. If you are a writer, that means—\n "
    },
    {
      "type": "blank",
      "blankId": 20
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": " ​\n—writing."
    }
  ],
